text: The white-tailed starfrontlet (Coeligena phalerata) is a species of hummingbird. It is found only in Colombia. Its habitat is subtropical or tropical moist montane forests. ==References== * BirdLife International 2004. Coeligena phalerata. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 10 July 2007.
